        "subject": "LU-10938 wbc: Intent open to create layout on MDT",
        "message": "LU-10938 wbc: Intent open to create layout on MDT\n\nFor a regular file under the protection of WBC EX lock (parent\nlocked), instante the file layout on MDT via intent open during\nmetadta flushing. This is important to be able to flush file data\nin the next step.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: If95250059a6a9c4289315f7829323f1e667c99f7\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\n"
